### 获取文章列表
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/articles
Authorization: {{token}}

### 获取单个文章
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/articles/1
Authorization: {{token}}

### 新增文章
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/articles
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{token}}
{
    "tag_id": 1,
    "title": "测试文章",
    "desc": "这是一篇测试文章",
    "content": "文章内容",
    "created_by": "admin",
    "state": 1
}

### 更新文章
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/articles/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{token}}

{
    "tag_id": "1",
    "title": "更新后的文章",
    "desc": "更新后的描述",
    "content": "更新后的内容",
    "modified_by": "admin",
    "state": 1
}

### 删除文章
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/articles/1
Authorization: {{token}}

